<p>Formatting dates can be tricky if you need a specific format. In this tutorial weâ€™ll show you how to build a date in almost any format.</p>

<h2 id="setup">Setup</h2>
<p>Weâ€™ll start by setting a date in front matter in ISO 8601 format.</p>
<pre class="highlight">
<code>
---
layout: default
title: Date Formatting
date: 2016-03-23T10:20:00Z
